726129f-a.title: Queens: Bayside Avenue - Union Street
726129f-a.text:
Bayside Avenue, north side, between Union Street and Parsons
Boulevard. The house and property was owned by Harriet Fisher
in 1909.
R2~13 A92

726130f-b.title: Queens: Bayside Avenue - Union Street
726130f-b.text:
Bayside Ave., at the S.E. corner of Union Street, showing in two
views, looking southeast, the Mitchell house which remained in the family
from 1804 to 1921. This is a set of two views.
April 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
